{"data":[{"name":"75:1","price":"われはまさに、復活の日*にかけて誓う。¹","arabic":"لَآ أُقۡسِمُ بِيَوۡمِ ٱلۡقِيَٰمَةِ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5552,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"１　この誓いについては、整列者章１の訳注を参照。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"lā uq'simu biyawmi al-qiyāmati ","translations":["Nay","I swear","by (the) Day","(of) the Resurrection","(1)"],"transliterationArr":["lā","uq'simu","biyawmi","al-qiyāmati",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2540],[2,2540,3370],[3,3370,4250],[4,4250,6015]]}},{"name":"75:2","price":"また、責め苛む魂¹にかけて誓う（、人々は蘇らされるのである、と）。","arabic":"وَلَآ أُقۡسِمُ بِٱلنَّفۡسِ ٱللَّوَّامَةِ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5553,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"１　死を迎える時、魂は、自分の行いを責める。一方、信仰者の魂は、義務の遂行における至らなさ、不注意などについて、現世で自分自身を責めるのである（アッ＝サアディー８９８頁参照）。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"walā uq'simu bil-nafsi al-lawāmati ","translations":["And nay","I swear","by the soul","self-accusing","(2)"],"transliterationArr":["walā","uq'simu","bil-nafsi","al-lawāmati",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2440],[2,2440,3280],[3,3280,5300],[4,5300,7415]]}},{"name":"75:3","price":"（不信仰な）人間は、われら*が彼の骨を（それが散り散りになった後に、）集めることが（出来）ない、とでも思っているのか？","arabic":"أَيَحۡسَبُ ٱلۡإِنسَٰنُ أَلَّن نَّجۡمَعَ عِظَامَهُۥ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5554,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"ayaḥsabu al-insānu allan najmaʿa ʿiẓāmahu ","translations":["Does think","[the] man","that not","We will assemble","his bones","(3)"],"transliterationArr":["ayaḥsabu","al-insānu","allan","najmaʿa","ʿiẓāmahu",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1070],[2,1070,3170],[3,3170,3850],[4,3850,5510],[5,5510,7155]]}},{"name":"75:4","price":"いや、われら*はその指先まで、きっちり整え（て組み立て、生前と同じ状態に復活させ）ることが出来る。","arabic":"بَلَىٰ قَٰدِرِينَ عَلَىٰٓ أَن نُّسَوِّيَ بَنَانَهُۥ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5555,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"balā qādirīna ʿalā an nusawwiya banānahu ","translations":["Nay","(We are) Able","on","that","We can restore","his fingertips","(4)"],"transliterationArr":["balā","qādirīna","ʿalā","an","nusawwiya","banānahu",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,690],[2,690,1960],[3,1960,3790],[4,3790,4080],[5,4080,5770],[6,5770,7395]]}},{"name":"75:5","price":"いや、（不信仰な）人間は、自らの前途において¹放逸であることを欲し（、復活を否定し）ている。","arabic":"بَلۡ يُرِيدُ ٱلۡإِنسَٰنُ لِيَفۡجُرَ أَمَامَهُۥ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5556,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"１　ほかにも、「自分自身の目的と欲望の追求において」「復活の日*が到来する前に」といった解釈もある（イブン・ジュザイ２：５１３参照）。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"bal yurīdu al-insānu liyafjura amāmahu ","translations":["Nay","Desires","[the] man","to give (the) lie","(to) what is before him","(5)"],"transliterationArr":["bal","yurīdu","al-insānu","liyafjura","amāmahu",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,450],[2,450,1230],[3,1230,3120],[4,3120,4170],[5,4170,5635]]}},{"name":"75:6","price":"「復活の日*は、一体いつなのか？」と尋ねながら。","arabic":"يَسۡـَٔلُ أَيَّانَ يَوۡمُ ٱلۡقِيَٰمَةِ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5557,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"yasalu ayyāna yawmu al-qiyāmati ","translations":["He asks","When","(is the) Day","(of) the Resurrection","(6)"],"transliterationArr":["yasalu","ayyāna","yawmu","al-qiyāmati",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,900],[2,900,1870],[3,1870,2540],[4,2540,4395]]}},{"name":"75:7","price":"（人々の）眼が（、復活の日*の恐怖によって）動転し、","arabic":"فَإِذَا بَرِقَ ٱلۡبَصَرُ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5558,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"fa-idhā bariqa al-baṣaru ","translations":["So when","is dazzled","the vision","(7)"],"transliterationArr":["fa-idhā","bariqa","al-baṣaru",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,870],[2,870,1480],[3,1480,2675]]}},{"name":"75:8","price":"月（の明かり）が消え、","arabic":"وَخَسَفَ ٱلۡقَمَرُ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5559,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"wakhasafa al-qamaru ","translations":["And becomes dark","the moon","(8)"],"transliterationArr":["wakhasafa","al-qamaru",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,860],[2,860,2005]]}},{"name":"75:9","price":"太陽と月が（共に暗くなって、）一緒くたにされる時、¹","arabic":"وَجُمِعَ ٱلشَّمۡسُ وَٱلۡقَمَرُ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5560,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"１　その他、「合わさって真っ黒な形で、西から同時に昇る」「一緒にされて海へと放り込まれ、海が燃え上がる」あるいは、地獄に「まとめて入れられる」といった解釈がある（アル＝クルトゥビー１９：９７参照）。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"wajumiʿa al-shamsu wal-qamaru ","translations":["And are joined","the sun","and the moon","(9)"],"transliterationArr":["wajumiʿa","al-shamsu","wal-qamaru",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,840],[2,840,1740],[3,1740,3075]]}},{"name":"75:10","price":"人間はその日、言う。「（懲罰からの）逃げ場所はどこだ？」","arabic":"يَقُولُ ٱلۡإِنسَٰنُ يَوۡمَئِذٍ أَيۡنَ ٱلۡمَفَرُّ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5561,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"yaqūlu al-insānu yawma-idhin ayna al-mafaru ","translations":["Will say","[the] man","that Day","Where","(is) the escape","(10)"],"transliterationArr":["yaqūlu","al-insānu","yawma-idhin","ayna","al-mafaru",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,820],[2,820,2870],[3,2870,4100],[4,4100,4660],[5,4660,6225]]}},{"name":"75:11","price":"断じて（、そうはいか）ない。避難場所など、ないのだ。","arabic":"كَلَّا لَا وَزَرَ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5562,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"kallā lā wazara ","translations":["By no means","(There is) no","refuge","(11)"],"transliterationArr":["kallā","lā","wazara",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,970],[2,970,1830],[3,1830,2865]]}},{"name":"75:12","price":"その日はあなたの主*にこそ、定住先があるのだから。","arabic":"إِلَىٰ رَبِّكَ يَوۡمَئِذٍ ٱلۡمُسۡتَقَرُّ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5563,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"ilā rabbika yawma-idhin al-mus'taqaru ","translations":["To","your Lord","that Day","(is) the place of rest","(12)"],"transliterationArr":["ilā","rabbika","yawma-idhin","al-mus'taqaru",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,680],[2,680,1450],[3,1450,2780],[4,2780,4625]]}},{"name":"75:13","price":"人間はその日、自分が（生きている時に）早めたものと、遅らせたもの¹について（全て）告げ聞かせられる。","arabic":"يُنَبَّؤُاْ ٱلۡإِنسَٰنُ يَوۡمَئِذِۭ بِمَا قَدَّمَ وَأَخَّرَ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5564,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"１　「早めたもの」と「遅らせたもの」の解釈には、「生前の小糸、死後に自分の行為を規範（きはん）として行われる他人の行為」「最初の行為と最後の行為」「前者が罪、後者が服従行為」といった諸説がある（前掲書１９：９８参照）。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"yunabba-u al-insānu yawma-idhin bimā qaddama wa-akhara ","translations":["Will be informed","[the] man","that Day","of what","he sent forth","and kept back","(13)"],"transliterationArr":["yunabba-u","al-insānu","yawma-idhin","bimā","qaddama","wa-akhara",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,990],[2,990,2990],[3,2990,4550],[4,4550,5490],[5,5490,6360],[6,6360,7915]]}},{"name":"75:14","price":"いや、人間は自分自身（が行ったこと）に対する、証人である。","arabic":"بَلِ ٱلۡإِنسَٰنُ عَلَىٰ نَفۡسِهِۦ بَصِيرَةٞ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5565,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"bali al-insānu ʿalā nafsihi baṣīratun ","translations":["Nay","[The] man","against","himself","(will be) a witness","(14)"],"transliterationArr":["bali","al-insānu","ʿalā","nafsihi","baṣīratun",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,440],[2,440,2320],[3,2320,2940],[4,2940,3910],[5,3910,5305]]}},{"name":"75:15","price":"たとえ、自分の（罪の）言い訳を申し立てても。","arabic":"وَلَوۡ أَلۡقَىٰ مَعَاذِيرَهُۥ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5566,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"walaw alqā maʿādhīrahu ","translations":["Even if","he presents","his excuses","(15)"],"transliterationArr":["walaw","alqā","maʿādhīrahu",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,630],[2,630,1450],[3,1450,3405]]}},{"name":"75:16","price":"——（預言者*よ、啓示が下った時には、）それ（クルアーン*の暗記）に急ぐがゆえに、（啓示が下りきる前に）あなたの舌を動かすのではない。¹","arabic":"لَا تُحَرِّكۡ بِهِۦ لِسَانَكَ لِتَعۡجَلَ بِهِۦٓ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5567,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"１　預言者*はジブリール*が啓示と共に訪れると、それを急いで受け取ろうと、躍起（やっき）になって口を動かしたものだった。それでアッラーは、彼がまずは啓示に耳を傾けるようご命じになり、暗記と読誦と説明については、アッラー*ご自身が保証されることを約束されたのだった。ター・ハー章１１４も参照（アル＝ブハーリー４９２７ー４９２９、イブン・カスィール８：２７８参照）。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"lā tuḥarrik bihi lisānaka litaʿjala bihi ","translations":["Not","move","with it","your tongue","to hasten","with it","(16)"],"transliterationArr":["lā","tuḥarrik","bihi","lisānaka","litaʿjala","bihi",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,400],[2,400,1460],[3,1460,2050],[4,2050,3090],[5,3090,4110],[6,4110,4985]]}},{"name":"75:17","price":"本当にそれを（あなたの胸に）結集させることと、それを（あなたが望む時にいつでも）読むこと（を可能にさせるの）は、われら*の任務なのだから。","arabic":"إِنَّ عَلَيۡنَا جَمۡعَهُۥ وَقُرۡءَانَهُۥ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5568,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"inna ʿalaynā jamʿahu waqur'ānahu ","translations":["Indeed","upon Us","(is) its collection","and its recitation","(17)"],"transliterationArr":["inna","ʿalaynā","jamʿahu","waqur'ānahu",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1270],[2,1270,2300],[3,2300,3390],[4,3390,5285]]}},{"name":"75:18","price":"それで、われら*がそれを（ジブリール*を介し、あなたに）読んだ時には、その読みに（まずはよく耳を傾け、それからその読誦に）続くのだ。","arabic":"فَإِذَا قَرَأۡنَٰهُ فَٱتَّبِعۡ قُرۡءَانَهُۥ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5569,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"fa-idhā qaranāhu fa-ittabiʿ qur'ānahu ","translations":["And when","We have recited it","then follow","its recitation","(18)"],"transliterationArr":["fa-idhā","qaranāhu","fa-ittabiʿ","qur'ānahu",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,800],[2,800,2080],[3,2080,3010],[4,3010,4615]]}},{"name":"75:19","price":"それから、実にわれら*にこそ、その（意味や法規定についての）説明義務があるのだ——。","arabic":"ثُمَّ إِنَّ عَلَيۡنَا بَيَانَهُۥ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5570,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"thumma inna ʿalaynā bayānahu ","translations":["Then","indeed","upon Us","(is) its explanation","(19)"],"transliterationArr":["thumma","inna","ʿalaynā","bayānahu",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1160],[2,1160,2320],[3,2320,3350],[4,3350,4865]]}},{"name":"75:20","price":"（シルク*の徒よ、）断じて（、復活と報いは嘘などでは）ない。いや、あなた方は手っ取り早いもの（現世）を愛し、","arabic":"كَلَّا بَلۡ تُحِبُّونَ ٱلۡعَاجِلَةَ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5571,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"kallā bal tuḥibbūna al-ʿājilata ","translations":["No","But","you love","the immediate","(20)"],"transliterationArr":["kallā","bal","tuḥibbūna","al-ʿājilata",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,860],[2,860,1190],[3,1190,2380],[4,2380,3905]]}},{"name":"75:21","price":"来世（のための行い）を放ったらかしにしている。¹","arabic":"وَتَذَرُونَ ٱلۡأٓخِرَةَ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5572,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"１　現世の享楽は手っ取り早く、来世（遅れるもの、という原義もあり）は永遠の安寧ながらも、遅れてやって来るもの（アッ＝サアディー８９９頁参照）。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"watadharūna al-ākhirata ","translations":["And leave","the Hereafter","(21)"],"transliterationArr":["watadharūna","al-ākhirata",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1220],[2,1220,2805]]}},{"name":"75:22","price":"（復活の）その日、（信仰者たちの）ほころびる顔は、","arabic":"وُجُوهٞ يَوۡمَئِذٖ نَّاضِرَةٌ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5573,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"wujūhun yawma-idhin nāḍiratun ","translations":["Faces","that Day","(will be) radiant","(22)"],"transliterationArr":["wujūhun","yawma-idhin","nāḍiratun",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,840],[2,840,1740],[3,1740,4735]]}},{"name":"75:23","price":"まさにその主*を眺める。¹","arabic":"إِلَىٰ رَبِّهَا نَاظِرَةٞ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5574,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"１　復活の日*、天国の民がアッラー*を拝見することについては、家畜章１０３とその訳注、ユーヌス*章２６、量を減らす者章１５も参照。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"ilā rabbihā nāẓiratun ","translations":["Towards","their Lord","looking","(23)"],"transliterationArr":["ilā","rabbihā","nāẓiratun",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,600],[2,600,1620],[3,1620,3065]]}},{"name":"75:24","price":"またその日、（不信仰者*たちの）しかめっ顔は、","arabic":"وَوُجُوهٞ يَوۡمَئِذِۭ بَاسِرَةٞ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5575,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"wawujūhun yawma-idhin bāsiratun ","translations":["And faces","that Day","(will be) distorted","(24)"],"transliterationArr":["wawujūhun","yawma-idhin","bāsiratun",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1130],[2,1130,3840],[3,3840,5285]]}},{"name":"75:25","price":"脊椎を破壊するほどの災禍が、自分たちに及ぼされることを確信する。","arabic":"تَظُنُّ أَن يُفۡعَلَ بِهَا فَاقِرَةٞ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5576,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"taẓunnu an yuf'ʿala bihā fāqiratun ","translations":["Thinking","that","will be done","to them","backbreaking","(25)"],"transliterationArr":["taẓunnu","an","yuf'ʿala","bihā","fāqiratun",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1670],[2,1670,1970],[3,1970,3550],[4,3550,4120],[5,4120,5655]]}},{"name":"75:26","price":"断じて（、復活と報いなどでは）ない！（死期が到来して、）それ（魂）が鎖骨まで達し、¹","arabic":"كَلَّآ إِذَا بَلَغَتِ ٱلتَّرَاقِيَ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5577,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"１　家畜章６１、９３とその訳注も参照。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"kallā idhā balaghati al-tarāqiya ","translations":["No","When","it reaches","the collar bones","(26)"],"transliterationArr":["kallā","idhā","balaghati","al-tarāqiya",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2230],[2,2230,2820],[3,2820,3760],[4,3760,5165]]}},{"name":"75:27","price":"（彼らの間で）「（この状態を）治してくれる者は、誰か？」と言われ、","arabic":"وَقِيلَ مَنۡۜ رَاقٖ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5578,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"waqīla man rāqin ","translations":["And it is said","Who","(will) cure","(27)"],"transliterationArr":["waqīla","man","rāqin",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,910],[2,910,1290],[3,1290,5045]]}},{"name":"75:28","price":"それがまさに（現世との）別離だと確信し、","arabic":"وَظَنَّ أَنَّهُ ٱلۡفِرَاقُ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5579,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"waẓanna annahu al-firāqu ","translations":["And he is certain","that it","(is) the parting","(28)"],"transliterationArr":["waẓanna","annahu","al-firāqu",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1470],[2,1470,2810],[3,2810,5615]]}},{"name":"75:29","price":"脛と脛が絡み合った時。¹","arabic":"وَٱلۡتَفَّتِ ٱلسَّاقُ بِٱلسَّاقِ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5580,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"１　この解釈には、「現世の最後における苦しみと、来世の始まりにおける苦しみが連続すること」「激しい苦しみゆえに、人の両足が絡み合う様」「死人の両足が、遺体を包む布で包まれること」といった諸説がある（アル＝クルトゥビー１９：１１２参照）。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"wal-tafati al-sāqu bil-sāqi ","translations":["And is wound","the leg","about the leg","(29)"],"transliterationArr":["wal-tafati","al-sāqu","bil-sāqi",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1270],[2,1270,2140],[3,2140,4855]]}},{"name":"75:30","price":"（復活の日*、）あなたの主*にこそ、連れられて行く先があるのである。","arabic":"إِلَىٰ رَبِّكَ يَوۡمَئِذٍ ٱلۡمَسَاقُ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5581,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"ilā rabbika yawma-idhin al-masāqu ","translations":["To","your Lord","that Day","(will be) the driving","(30)"],"transliterationArr":["ilā","rabbika","yawma-idhin","al-masāqu",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,570],[2,570,1380],[3,1380,2620],[4,2620,6075]]}},{"name":"75:31","price":"彼（不信仰者*）は、（使徒*もクルアーン*も）信じなければ、礼拝もしなかった。","arabic":"فَلَا صَدَّقَ وَلَا صَلَّىٰ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5582,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"falā ṣaddaqa walā ṣallā ","translations":["And not","he accepted (the) truth","and not","he prayed","(31)"],"transliterationArr":["falā","ṣaddaqa","walā","ṣallā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,600],[2,600,1500],[3,1500,1980],[4,1980,3045]]}},{"name":"75:32","price":"それどころか（クルアーン*を）噓呼ばわりし、（信仰から）背いた。","arabic":"وَلَٰكِن كَذَّبَ وَتَوَلَّىٰ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5583,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"walākin kadhaba watawallā ","translations":["But","he denied","and turned away","(32)"],"transliterationArr":["walākin","kadhaba","watawallā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1710],[2,1710,2540],[3,2540,3815]]}},{"name":"75:33","price":"それから自分の家族のもとへ、闊歩しつつ¹向かったのだ。","arabic":"ثُمَّ ذَهَبَ إِلَىٰٓ أَهۡلِهِۦ يَتَمَطَّىٰٓ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5584,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"１　これはつまり、尊大さ、高慢さを示す歩き方のこと。このアーヤ*は一説に、自分の出身部族であるマフズーム族の中でそのようにして歩くことが知られていた、アブー・ジャハル*について下った（イブン・ジュザイ２：５１５参照）。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"thumma dhahaba ilā ahlihi yatamaṭṭā ","translations":["Then","he went","to","his family","swaggering","(33)"],"transliterationArr":["thumma","dhahaba","ilā","ahlihi","yatamaṭṭā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1180],[2,1180,1910],[3,1910,3460],[4,3460,4530],[5,4530,6245]]}},{"name":"75:34","price":"あなたに、もっと（破滅が）近づくよう、もっと（破滅が）近づくよう。","arabic":"أَوۡلَىٰ لَكَ فَأَوۡلَىٰ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5585,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"awlā laka fa-awlā ","translations":["Woe","to you","and woe","(34)"],"transliterationArr":["awlā","laka","fa-awlā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,830],[2,830,1180],[3,1180,2335]]}},{"name":"75:35","price":"更に、あなたにもっと（破滅が）近づくよう、もっと（破滅が）近づくよう。¹","arabic":"ثُمَّ أَوۡلَىٰ لَكَ فَأَوۡلَىٰٓ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5586,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"１　一説にこのアーヤ*は、ある時アブー・ジャハル*から嫌がらせを受けた預言者*が彼に対して言った言葉が、後にそのまま啓示として下ったもの（イブン・カスィール８：２８３参照）。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"thumma awlā laka fa-awlā ","translations":["Then","woe","to you","and woe","(35)"],"transliterationArr":["thumma","awlā","laka","fa-awlā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1220],[2,1220,2090],[3,2090,2420],[4,2420,3595]]}},{"name":"75:36","price":"一体、（復活を否定する）人間は、（命令も禁止もされず、報いも懲罰もなく、）放ったらかしにされるとでも思っているのか？","arabic":"أَيَحۡسَبُ ٱلۡإِنسَٰنُ أَن يُتۡرَكَ سُدًى","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5587,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"ayaḥsabu al-insānu an yut'raka sudan ","translations":["Does think","man","that","he will be left","neglected","(36)"],"transliterationArr":["ayaḥsabu","al-insānu","an","yut'raka","sudan",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,980],[2,980,3230],[3,3230,3600],[4,3600,5110],[5,5110,5965]]}},{"name":"75:37","price":"彼は、（子宮へ）注がれる精液の一滴ではなかったのか？","arabic":"أَلَمۡ يَكُ نُطۡفَةٗ مِّن مَّنِيّٖ يُمۡنَىٰ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5588,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"alam yaku nuṭ'fatan min maniyyin yum'nā ","translations":["Was not","he","a semen-drop","of","semen","emitted","(37)"],"transliterationArr":["alam","yaku","nuṭ'fatan","min","maniyyin","yum'nā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,550],[2,550,1050],[3,1050,1960],[4,1960,2870],[5,2870,5280],[6,5280,6235]]}},{"name":"75:38","price":"それから一塊の凝血となり、そしてかれがお創りになって、（その姿形を最も美しく）整えられ、","arabic":"ثُمَّ كَانَ عَلَقَةٗ فَخَلَقَ فَسَوَّىٰ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5589,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"thumma kāna ʿalaqatan fakhalaqa fasawwā ","translations":["Then","he was","a clinging substance","then He created","and proportioned","(38)"],"transliterationArr":["thumma","kāna","ʿalaqatan","fakhalaqa","fasawwā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1420],[2,1420,2030],[3,2030,3550],[4,3550,4410],[5,4410,5595]]}},{"name":"75:39","price":"そこから二種類、つまり男性と女性をお創りになったのでは？","arabic":"فَجَعَلَ مِنۡهُ ٱلزَّوۡجَيۡنِ ٱلذَّكَرَ وَٱلۡأُنثَىٰٓ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5590,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"fajaʿala min'hu al-zawjayni al-dhakara wal-unthā ","translations":["Then made","of him","two kinds","(the) male","and the female","(39)"],"transliterationArr":["fajaʿala","min'hu","al-zawjayni","al-dhakara","wal-unthā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,800],[2,800,1370],[3,1370,2670],[4,2670,3490],[5,3490,5655]]}},{"name":"75:40","price":"一体（それらの創造主である）そのお方（アッラー*）は、死者に（再び）生をお与えになることが出来るお方なのではないか？","arabic":"أَلَيۡسَ ذَٰلِكَ بِقَٰدِرٍ عَلَىٰٓ أَن يُحۡـِۧيَ ٱلۡمَوۡتَىٰ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5591,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"alaysa dhālika biqādirin ʿalā an yuḥ'yiya al-mawtā ","translations":["Is not","[that]","(He) Able","[over]","to","give life","(to) the dead","(40)"],"transliterationArr":["alaysa","dhālika","biqādirin","ʿalā","an","yuḥ'yiya","al-mawtā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,890],[2,890,1660],[3,1660,2800],[4,2800,4549],[5,4549,4769],[6,4769,5819],[7,5819,8084]]}}],"chapter":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah","Chapter Al-Qiyamah","Qiyamah","Surah Qiyamah","Chapter Qiyamah","Al Qiyamah","Surah Al Qiyamah","Chapter Al Qiyamah","Surah 75","Chapter 75","The Resurrection","القيامة"],"version":{"key":"japanese_saeedsato","direction":"ltr","language_iso_code":"ja","version":"1.0.10","last_update":1709035504,"title":"Japanese translation - Saeed Sato","description":"Translation of the Quran meanings into Japanese by Saeed Sato. printed in 1440 H."}}